<H3> <TI>   Awards to Medical, Other Personnel </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94UM0253A Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 22 Feb 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 94UM0253A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>


