------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Weight of the incendiary-smoke mixtur-|2.3                                   | 
|e, kg                                 |                                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Number of flamethrowers in a pack, un-|2                                     | 
|its                                   |                                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Crew                                  |1 man                                 | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Weight of the pack, kg                |22                                    | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 



