from an English military annual): 
  Tanks--1,850 
  Armored vehicles--1,390 
  Warplanes--716 
  Helicopters--80 
  Composition: Emphasis is laid on creating 
airborne assault and airborne-ground-attack units, mechanized 
brigades and air regiments. 
  Combat 
